er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">I wrote the other day</a> that =E2=80=9Cthe b=
asic innovation of crypto is the production of artificial scarcity,=E2=80=
